                        </li>
                        <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
                            <span class="text-green-400 shrink-0">✓</span> Botón WhatsApp
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
                            <span class="text-green-400 shrink-0">✓</span> Carga Instantánea
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
                            <span class="text-green-400 shrink-0">✓</span> Hosting
                            <strong>GRATIS</strong> (1 año)
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div
                class="relative group h-full scale-100 md:scale-105 z-10 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-500 animate-on-scroll fade-up"
            >
                <div
                    class="absolute -inset-0.5 bg-gradient-to-b from-primary to-orange-600 rounded-3xl blur opacity-40 group-hover:opacity-70 transition duration-500"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                    class="relative bg-[#151515] backdrop-blur-xl border border-primary/50 rounded-3xl p-6 flex flex-col h-full shadow-2xl"
                >
                    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4">
                        <span
                            class="bg-primary text-white text-[10px] font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider shadow-[0_0_15px_#FF6363]"
                            >Más Popular</span
                        >
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="font-fact text-2xl text-white mb-2 mt-2">
                        Corporate Pro
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-6 min-h-[40px]">
                        Sitio completo multisección para generar autoridad.
                    </p>
                    <div class="flex items-baseline gap-1 mb-6">
                        <span class="text-5xl font-bold text-white">399€</span>
                        <span
                            class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase font-bold tracking-wider"
                            >/ pago único</span
                        >
                    </div>
                    <a
                        href="#contacto"
                        class="w-full bg-white text-black font-bold py-3.5 rounded-xl text-center hover:bg-gray-200 transition-all mb-8 shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(255,255,255,0.3)] hover:scale-[1.02]"
                        >Empezar Ahora</a
                    >
                    <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm text-gray-300 flex-grow">
                        <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
                            <span class="text-green-400 shrink-0">✓</span> Hasta <strong
                                >5 Secciones</strong
                            >
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
                            <span class="text-green-400 shrink-0">✓</span> Arquitectura
                            <strong>Sin Plantillas</strong>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
                            <span class="text-green-400 shrink-0">✓</span> SEO Técnico
                            Avanzado
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
                            <span class="text-green-400 shrink-0">✓</span> Seguridad
                            Avanzada
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
                            <span class="text-green-400 shrink-0">✓</span> Dominio
                            + Hosting <strong>GRATIS</strong> (1 año)
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div
                class="relative group h-full hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-500 animate-on-scroll from-right delay-100"
            >
                <div
                    class="absolute -inset-0.5 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/10 to-transparent rounded-3xl blur opacity-30 group-hover:opacity-50 transition duration-500"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                    class="relative bg-[#0F0F0F]/95 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/10 rounded-3xl p-6 flex flex-col h-full hover:border-white/30 transition-colors shadow-lg"
                >
                    <h3 class="font-fact text-2xl text-white mb-2">
                        CORPORATE ELITE
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-6 min-h-[40px]">
                        Experiencia digital de alto impacto. Domina tu sector
                        con tecnología punta.
                    </p>
                    <div class="flex items-baseline gap-2 mb-6">
                        <span class="text-xl text-gray-400">desde</span>
                        <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-white">599€</span>
                        <span
                            class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase font-bold tracking-wider"
                            >/ pago único</span
                        >
                    </div>
                    <a
                        href="#contacto"
                        class="w-full bg-white/5 text-white font-bold py-3 rounded-xl text-center hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition-all mb-8 border border-white/10 group-hover:border-white/40"
                        >Solicitar Información</a
                    >
                    <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm text-gray-300 flex-grow">
                        <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
                            <span class="text-green-400 shrink-0">✓</span>
                            <strong>Scroll Interactivo</strong>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
                            <span class="text-green-400 shrink-0">✓</span> SEO de
                            Contenidos Avanzado
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
                            <span class="text-green-400 shrink-0">✓</span> Analítica
                            Mensual (GA4)
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
                            <span class="text-green-400 shrink-0">✓</span> Hasta 10
                            secciones
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
                            <span class="text-green-400 shrink-0">✓</span> Dominio
                            + Hosting <strong>GRATIS</strong> (1 año)
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div
            class="relative w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-8 group animate-on-scroll fade-up delay-200"
        >
            <div
                class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-900 via-slate-800 to-blue-900 rounded-2xl blur opacity-20 group-hover:opacity-40 transition duration-1000"
            >
            </div>
            <div
                class="relative bg-[#0F0F0F]/90 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6 overflow-hidden"
            >
                <div
                    class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-blue-500/10 rounded-full blur-[80px] -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2 pointer-events-none"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                    class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center md:items-start text-center md:text-left gap-5 relative z-10 w-full"
                >
                    <div
                        class="p-4 bg-white/5 rounded-xl text-white shrink-0 border border-white/5 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500"
                    >
                        <svg
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                            width="32"
                            height="32"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            fill="none"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            stroke-width="1.5"
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            ><path
                                d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"
                            ></path></svg
                        >
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-grow">
                        <h4 class="font-fact text-2xl text-white mb-2">
                            Mantenimiento & Soporte
                        </h4>
                        <p
                            class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-4 max-w-md mx-auto md:mx-0"
                        >
                            Monitorización 24/7, cambios mensuales y <strong
                                >renovación anual de Dominio y Hosting</strong
                            >.
                        </p>
                        <p
                            class="text-xs text-gray-500 italic border-t border-white/5 pt-2"
                        >
                            * Sin suscripción: cambios puntuales a <strong
                                class="text-gray-300">80€/intervención</strong
                            >.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="flex flex-col items-center md:items-end gap-3 relative z-10 w-full md:w-auto shrink-0 border-t md:border-t-0 md:border-l border-white/10 pt-4 md:pt-0 md:pl-6"
                >
                    <div class="text-center md:text-right">
                        <span class="block text-4xl font-bold text-white"
                            >39€</span
                        >
                        <span
                            class="text-xs text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider"
                            >/mes</span
                        >
                    </div>
                    <a
                        href="#contacto"
                        class="bg-white text-black hover:bg-gray-200 font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-xl transition-all shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transform hover:-translate-y-0.5 whitespace-nowrap text-sm"
                        >Contratar Mantenimiento</a
                    >
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
